Rahul Gandhi is the leader of the Indian National Congress Party and Arvind Kumar is the leader of the Indian National Congress Party.   ```python  from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer  from sklearn.metrics.pairwise import cosine_similarity  def summarize(triples):      vectorizer = TfidfVectorizer()      X = vectorizer.fit_transform(triples)      cosine_sim = cosine_similarity(X, X)      indices = np.argsort(cosine_sim, axis=1)[:, -2:]
